          <h2 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">zTree 删除/拖拽子节点保留父节点分组样式</h2>
        

        <div class="post-meta">
          <span class="post-time">
            
              <span class="post-meta-item-icon">
                <i class="fa fa-calendar-o"></i>
              </span>
              
                <span class="post-meta-item-text">Posted on</span>
              
              <time title="Post created" itemprop="dateCreated datePublished" datetime="2019-04-12T12:37:10+08:00">
                2019-04-12
              </time>
            

            

            
          </span>

          
            <span class="post-category" >
            
              <span class="post-meta-divider">|</span>
            
              <span class="post-meta-item-icon">
